9️⃣ DevOps Best Practices Learned
✅ Do NOT use hostPath in production (EKS)

Use:

EBS via StorageClass

Dynamic provisioning

✅ Always upgrade MongoDB step-by-step:
4.0 → 4.2 → 4.4 → 5.0 → 6.0
✅ Avoid hardcoding image in templates

Use Helm values:

values.yaml:

image:
  repository: mongo
  tag: "6.0"

template:

image: "{{ .Values.image.repository }}:{{ .Values.image.tag }}"
✅ Always verify image after deployment
kubectl describe pod | grep Image
